{"tid":1758800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家知唔知聽日星期四有咩行動呢？","createTime":"2019-11-27T09:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T17:46:22.000Z","uid":256181,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4617abf42f02789d2d001addeaaa483254431ba","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔知嘅話就一齊過嚟推po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知嘅話⋯⋯都一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">1.1900愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「香港民主人權法案」集會</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(有不反對通知書)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.1930維園</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">國際人權日集會</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.1930尖沙咀鐘樓<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">反對理大大圍捕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(有不反對通知書)</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.1400-1800遮打花園<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">家長守護你集氣會</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>四揀一任君選擇，<br />\n唔係唔去呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抖左兩日已經抖夠，<br />\n係時候推番行動post，<br />\n繼續keep住團火！<br />\n即刻跟我大嗌一次：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGrGJrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGrGJrz.jpg&h=5b91ec24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owaXn1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowaXn1N.jpg&h=f389d950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f327efd02082b1510ce74e344bdf85ae4eb005","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f11caef8588b6d2936ce5e7236862d9eba527f","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8dea3f9a11b61a26ae432e9321118f8c968fc0","tid":1758800,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8939d26c70b962eb4a12f947c98f55e473bdfda","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c723217cbee3696b06fa9d9c7d980d52ead5e374","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c8dea3f9a11b61a26ae432e9321118f8c968fc0","tid":1758800,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝"},{"pid":"1a2c67008fa52dcbcb7a4333cfceebe66a6e5694","tid":1758800,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited